<div class="panel">
	<h3><i class="icon-shield"></i> {l s='Google Consent Mode' mod='freega4'}</h3>
	<div class="alert alert-info">
		<p>
			<strong>{l s='Google Consent Mode is managed by your cookie banner.' mod='freega4'}</strong>
		</p>
		<p>
			{l s='This module does not include a consent manager bridge because modern cookie banners usually provide Google Consent Mode v2 directly.' mod='freega4'}
		</p>
		<p>
			{l s='Before enabling GA4 tracking, configure Google Consent Mode in your cookie solution, such as LG Cookies Law, Art Cookie Choices Pro, iubenda, Cookiebot or a similar CMP.' mod='freega4'}
		</p>
		<p>
			{l s='Only one system should update Google consent signals for analytics_storage, ad_storage, ad_user_data and ad_personalization.' mod='freega4'}
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
